flowchart LR
    REPO[Repository] --> CI[CI Pipeline]
    CI --> SCAN[Policy + Dependency Scan]
    CI --> SIGN[Artifact Signing]
    SIGN --> REG[Artifact Registry]
    REG --> VERIFY[Provenance Verification Gate]
    VERIFY --> CD[Deploy Pipeline]
    CD --> PROD[Production]

    PIN[Immutable Action Pinning] --> CI
    LEAST[Least-Privilege Tokens] --> CI
    EPH[Ephemeral Runner Controls] --> CI

    NOTE1[Only signed/proven artifacts can deploy]
    NOTE2[Workflow drift blocked by policy gate]

    VERIFY -.-> NOTE1
    SCAN -.-> NOTE2
